libhildonfm (1:2.20) unstable; urgency=low

  * Updated: Split the local device visibility handling again so that we have a callback for mounted and unmounted each, and check the device URI more carefully as it turns out the previous changes were based on wrong assumptions.
  * Fixes: NB#123719 HildonFileChooserDialog blocks other windows in multi stack application
  * Fixes: NB#116136 POSIX, Incorrect date format in details dialog.
  * Updated: Merge the handling of the visibility of the local device into one function.
  * Fixes: NB#122980 Folder can not be changed in 'Location' field when mmc card was removed
  * Updated: Obtain the volume from the path via GnomeVfs instead of iterating over all devices.
  * Updated: Revise navigation_pane_filter_func to be more redable.

 -- Mikko Tuhkanen <mikko.tuhkanen@d\igia.com>  Fri, 26 Jun 2009 12:24:58 +0300

