  * debian/rules: Removed unused version magic.  Dont attempt to copy
    config.sub and config.guess from /usr/share/misc on clean.  Don't
    cleanup outo bits, since outo is not used anymore.  Removed
    --disable-gtk-doc from configure options.
  * debian/control: Added gtk-doc-tools to Build-Depends and removed outo.
    Include major version in -dev package.  Removed -test package.
    Don't let the -dev package conflict with the old hildon-fm-dev.
  
