hildon-fm (1.7-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed column width problems. Patch from Tapani P√§lli. Fixes: NB#34618
  * Fixed the ever-lasting updating banner by using a timeout to close it.
    Fixes: NB#32064
  * Made an optimisation to file banner showing -- now it does not generate
    a flood of D-Bus activity when scanning a file list.
  * Added handling of an unexpected files-added signal. Fixes: NB#38523
  * Corrected destination path in items-dropped signal. Fixes: NB#38406
  * Included a change required by fixed OBEX module (thus depends on new
    osso-gnomevfs-extra).

 -- Kimmo H√§m√§l√§inen <kimmo.hamalainen@nokia.com>  Thu, 31 Aug 2006 19:02:02 +0300

