 -- Kuisma Salonen <kuisma.salonen@nokia.com>  Mon, 10 Jul 2006 18:16:14 +0300

hildon-fm (1.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Some Lintian fixes. (Kimmo)
  * Fixed logical strings used in the Details dialog when showing file sizes.
    (Kimmo)
  * Corrected localisation domain for ckdg_ti_new_folder. Fixes: NB#33863
    (Kimmo)
  * Fixed a bug in unit testing code. Fixes: NB#32579 (Kimmo)
  * Added system to look up BT device nicknames. Fixes: NB#33840
  * Removed hack to unescape the uri and made one to allow unescaping locally,
    the uri is now unescaped within the child class.
  * Exchanged hildon-file-system-bt.* with hildon-file-system-obex.*.
  * The problem with listing OBEX devices (the unneccessary probing) is
    solved. Fixes: NB#34017

 -- Kuisma Salonen <kuisma.salonen@nokia.com>  Fri,  7 Jul 2006 17:30:42 +0300

hildon-fm (1.2-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * (This is fixed changelog entry, otherwise same as 1.2-1.)
  * Added support for multiple Bluetooth devices.
  * Added some missing license texts and fixed some white space.
  * Fixed some localised strings. Fixes: NB#33233
  * Added missing if statement. Fixes: NB#33126, NB#33391, NB#27008
  * Fixed too persistent Updating banner when deleting files from Gateway.
  * Now moving selection to Gateway before trying to connect to it.
    Fixes: NB#29953
  * Fixed names of memory cards when the localised name is used.
    Fixes: NB#31299, NB#32411

