 -- Kimmo H√§m√§l√§inen <kimmo.hamalainen@nokia.com>  Tue, 30 May 2006 14:50:44 +0300

hildon-fm (1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Made branch to trunk and maintenance branch.
  * Major refactoring of code, and initial UPnP/AV support.
  * Corrected sfil_ni_operation_failed to sfil_ib_create_folder_not_allowed
    (N#29064).
  * Some white space & indentation fixes.
  * Fixed small UI glitch ('(no notes)') (N#22670).
  * Now showing correct icon while generating thumbnail for images (N#29799).
    (This introduced libossomime dependency.)
  * Added hildon_file_chooser_dialog_focus_to_input for special selection
    needs (N#28539).
  * Fixed unparenting problem in file selection finalisation (N#28074).
  * Fixed reporting of file size in the details dialog (N#30373, N#30380).
  * Fixed linking to libossomime library (N#30315).

