hildon-fm (0.21-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Backported hildon_file_system_info_async_new() and
    hildon_file_system_info_async_cancel() to enable easier moving to
    the new asyncronous API.
  * Added two unit tests for the asyncronous API.
  * hildon-fm-dev is for all architecture (N#27025).
  * hildon-fm-test is for all architecture (N#27026).
  * Lintian fixes.

